{"image_id": "FMC_2003_page_14", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "PART I", "bbox": [602.5, 157.8, 672.4, 178.7]}, {"text": "FMC Corporation (“FMC”) was incorporated in 1928 under Delaware law and has its principal executive", "bbox": [204.2, 208.1, 1112.4, 228.9]}, {"text": "offices at 1735 Market Street, Philadelphia, Pennsylvania 19103. As used in this report, except where otherwise", "bbox": [162.5, 233.1, 1112.4, 253.9]}, {"text": "stated or indicated by the context, FMC or the company means FMC Corporation and its consolidated", "bbox": [162.5, 258.1, 1112.2, 278.9]}, {"text": "subsidiaries and their predecessors.", "bbox": [162.5, 283.1, 456.8, 303.9]}, {"text": "ITEM 1.", "bbox": [162.5, 345.3, 238.8, 366.2]}, {"text": "BUSINESS", "bbox": [259.7, 345.3, 360.4, 366.2]}, {"text": "General", "bbox": [162.5, 382.8, 234.2, 403.7]}, {"text": "We are a diversified, global chemical company providing innovative solutions, applications and market-", "bbox": [204.2, 420.6, 1112.3, 441.4]}, {"text": "leading products to a wide variety of end markets. We operate in three distinct business segments: Agricultural", "bbox": [162.5, 445.6, 1112.2, 466.4]}, {"text": "Products, Specialty Chemicals and Industrial Chemicals. Agricultural Products’ focus is on insecticides, which", "bbox": [162.5, 470.6, 1112.5, 491.4]}, {"text": "are used to enhance crop yield and quality by controlling a wide spectrum of pests, and on herbicides, which are", "bbox": [162.5, 495.6, 1112.4, 516.4]}, {"text": "used to reduce the need for manual or mechanical weeding by inhibiting or preventing weed growth. Specialty", "bbox": [162.5, 520.6, 1112.4, 541.4]}, {"text": "Chemicals consists of our BioPolymer and lithium businesses and focuses on food ingredients that are used to", "bbox": [162.5, 545.6, 1112.5, 566.4]}, {"text": "enhance texture, structure and physical stability, pharmaceutical additives for binding and disintegrant use and", "bbox": [162.5, 570.6, 1112.5, 591.4]}, {"text": "lithium specialties for pharmaceutical synthesis and energy storage. Our Industrial Chemicals segment", "bbox": [162.5, 595.6, 1112.4, 616.4]}, {"text": "manufactures a wide range of inorganic materials, including soda ash, hydrogen peroxide, specialty peroxygens", "bbox": [162.5, 620.6, 1112.4, 641.4]}, {"text": "and phosphorus chemicals.", "bbox": [162.5, 645.6, 387.6, 666.4]}, {"text": "The following table shows the principal products produced by our three business segments and their raw", "bbox": [204.2, 695.6, 1112.4, 716.4]}, {"text": "materials and uses:", "bbox": [162.5, 720.6, 321.3, 741.4]}, {"text": "Segment", "bbox": [162.5, 753.7, 238.8, 774.5]}, {"text": "Product", "bbox": [391.7, 753.7, 463.4, 774.5]}, {"text": "Raw Materials", "bbox": [550.6, 753.7, 681.8, 774.5]}, {"text": "Uses", "bbox": [778.9, 753.7, 819.3, 774.5]}, {"text": "Agricultural Products", "bbox": [162.5, 787.2, 342.7, 808.1]}, {"text": "Insecticides", "bbox": [391.7, 787.2, 490.0, 808.1]}, {"text": "Synthetic chemical", "bbox": [550.6, 787.2, 709.9, 808.1]}, {"text": "intermediates", "bbox": [571.5, 812.2, 683.7, 833.1]}, {"text": "Protection of row crops, rice,", "bbox": [778.9, 787.2, 1022.2, 808.1]}, {"text": "sugarcane, cereals, fruits and", "bbox": [799.7, 812.2, 1041.4, 833.1]}, {"text": "vegetables from insects and for non-", "bbox": [799.7, 837.2, 1104.0, 858.1]}, {"text": "agricultural structural pest control", "bbox": [799.7, 862.2, 1083.3, 883.1]}, {"text": "Herbicides", "bbox": [391.7, 887.2, 481.9, 908.1]}, {"text": "Synthetic chemical", "bbox": [550.6, 887.2, 709.9, 908.1]}, {"text": "intermediates", "bbox": [571.5, 912.2, 683.7, 933.1]}, {"text": "Protection of row crops, rice,", "bbox": [778.9, 887.2, 1022.2, 908.1]}, {"text": "sugarcane, cereals, vegetables, turf", "bbox": [799.7, 912.2, 1090.6, 933.1]}, {"text": "and roadsides from weed growth", "bbox": [799.7, 937.2, 1073.1, 958.1]}, {"text": "Specialty Chemicals", "bbox": [162.5, 974.7, 333.3, 995.6]}, {"text": "M